{"tid":1916444,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"比個新仔話我地公司仲用Email好落後","createTime":"2020-03-09T01:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T13:46:38.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8d9ccc64adc520fae152f10808ed5ab63dc1e7","tid":1916444,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"星期五嗰日嚟咗個新Office Boy，<br />\n啱啱中六畢業冇上去就出嚟做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n當同佢做緊Orientation，<br />\n講到公司會每月有生日會，<br />\n而日子同詳情會用Email通知大家果陣，<br />\n佢突然彈句：「咩你地公司仲用Email咁落後嘅？我個Email都差唔多幾萬封未睇，咩原來呢個年代真係仲有人用Email？」<br />\n我就反問咁唔用Email應該用乜？<br />\n佢竟然答：「點解唔用微信？開個Group有咩係入面講咪得」<br />\n<br />\n其實中學生都應該知道Email先係正式嘅通訊方式啦下話？況且用Email又有幾落後呢？用微信都唔見得好先進？"},{"pid":"0bcd8a8f3ed26110efc6537cff1e5d3dd3e721c2","tid":1916444,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"又出潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前睇過啦"},{"pid":"03330cdc8435b2bf6c4dadf5eb413ddbbd635a00","tid":1916444,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"中學畢業都敢請，咩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545eca9c25ae6261c1c7411c0f2f32c77f4705ce","tid":1916444,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:31:22.000Z","msg":"下，仲有人用email既咩？<br />\n我公司用下snapchat, 同事做野即刻上心左， 快左<br />\n如果老細見到冇🔥冇❤️， 即刻收warning"},{"pid":"11743110449a22f8800701f9ad52d50573db6ea6","tid":1916444,"uid":252373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"545eca9c25ae6261c1c7411c0f2f32c77f4705ce","tid":1916444,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:31:22.000Z","msg":"下，仲有人用email既咩？<br />\n我公司用下snapchat, 同事做野即刻上心左， 快左<br />\n如果老細見到冇🔥冇❤️， 即刻收warning"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"仆得街<br />\n<br />\n好撚難❤️<br />\n仲要得一個<br />\n<br />\n間公司執硬"}]}